asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2012 or 2013 Jeep Wrangler 3.6L.

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=63-1566

K&N 63-1566 air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 12 horsepower at 5600 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. 

K&N 63-1566 fits the following: 
2014 JEEP WRANGLER 3.6L V6 
2013 JEEP WRANGLER 3.6L V6  
2012 JEEP WRANGLER 3.6L V6 

Go to http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=63-1566 for an up to date vehicle application list.

To search for your own vehicle's corresponding cold air intake and air filter visit
http://www.KNfilters.com
